Description:
"TableTop Soccer is a tactical, turn-based, online multiplayer/single player game. With a heavy focus on strategy & tactics, play solo games, challenge friends, or players all over the world. Play live games or play resumable games over a few days to perfect your plan. Earn experience points scoring goals & winning games to level up your players, unlock abilities and customize your team to try to take the top spot on the Leaderboards.

You'll need to think fast and plan ahead to anticipate your opponent, react quickly and not succumb to pressure to crush your opponents' dreams and bring your team to victory.

Game Features:
*Compete online with players all over the world in live games;

*Challenge Friends to play online games;

*Play quick Live games, or play Resumable games over a few days – getting Notifications whenever it's your turn;

*Practice your technique against the AI Team “Evil Machines”;

*Simultaneous Turns - In live games, both players take their turn at the same time - make your moves before the timer runs out! 

*Earn points by winning games and scoring goals to upgrade the skills & abilities of your players to make the perfect team that matches your play style;

*Watch Replays of full games - your own games and those of other players, to learn new tricks and tips; 

*Climb the Leaderboards and level up your team from Novice to Master; 

*True Cross-Platform Multiplayer - All platforms play on the same servers;

*Get Mobile notifications when any Resumable game is ready for you to jump in;

**Requires an internet connection to play;"

Welcome to the Viking age in the exciting strategy Vikings Odyssey. Build a viking settlement on the edge of known world and let it thrive!

You are a Norse chief, and rather notorious one. You had caused problems in Norway, so the king forced you to move to Iceland. You had some misunderstandings with local folk there, and eventually you were exiled to Greenland. But it was too boring for you in those cold wildlands, so you decided to move further.

According to the sagas, there was a distant land in the West - Vinland…

You had gathered three longships and two dozen fair families. One month in the sea passed away - and here you are! A new land to settle - a new place to call home.

Expand your settlement: build and improve buildings, gather resources, gain influence… and become the King of Vinland!

• Collect necessary resources;
• Build and upgrade new buildings;
• Bring prosperity to your settlement;
• Сlaim these land as your realm;
• Protect your village from enemies.

"Battle Cards, a free-to-play strategy game is loved by many people for its combination of simple action based gameplay and variable tactics. Alongside with well-developed social features it's known to be a good time killer.

Command powerful, futuristic armies and high tech weaponry. Choose The Brotherhood: Sworn to defend humanity, or the Cult: a sect obsessed with alien technology. Battle your friends, or team up with them, and fight to become a Legend.

Some very cool features are:
1) free to play;
2) two factions: Brotherhood and Cult with 50 unique cards;
3) more than 100 animated cards to battle with;
4) 15 ranks to achieve (from civilian to Legend);
6) configurable deck;
7) dozens of upgrades and artifacts;
8) local and global chat;
9) multiple achievements;
10) weekly tournaments with free registration;
11) various arenas to fight;

Official website: http://playbattlecards.com
Copyright @ 2013 3way Interactive. http://3wayint.com"

