Tap on groups of bubbles to blast them. Bust bigger groups of bubbles to get more points.
To win you must have a very well-thought strategy. You can try to form bigger groups by busting the smaller groups first. Then when you destroy these bigger groups you get special bubbles. You can use them to bust more bubbles, not just the bubbles belonging to a group. For every level, especially for the more advanced, you will need to adapt your strategy based on what bubbles you have on the board.

Download and play now!

● ● ● FEATURES ● ● ●

- 340+ hand-crafted levels, each one unique and filled with amazing challenges;

- 2 types of levels: levels with limited moves and levels with a time limit;

- 2 game objectives: achieve the target score and break all diamond and crystal cells;

- Multipliers, silver coins, golden coins and diamonds placed above the bubbles which will help you get more points;

- 3 types of obstacles: stones, rocks and bars;

- HD quality graphics that will look great on your phone and tablet;

- Addictive, suitably challenging as you move up through the levels;

- Bubble Buster Quest is completely free to play. You can complete all levels without making a single purchase. However, if you want to speed up your progress, you can make in-app purchases to get extra moves, time or lives. The account owner should always be consulted beforehand. By downloading this game, you confirm that you agree to our terms of service: http://www.gsoftteam.com/eula

